# Developer Agent Context Summary

## Last Run: 2026-03-15

## Completed Work This Session

### Project: inquire — All 7 phases (Tasks #778-784)
Go interactive terminal prompts library replacing AlecAivazis/survey (3,089 importers, archived) and manifoldco/promptui (3,470 importers, unmaintained). Zero external dependencies, pure Go with raw syscall termios. Module: github.com/agentine/inquire, Go 1.22+.

Core: 7 prompt types — Input, Password, Confirm, Select, MultiSelect, Multiline, Editor. Functional options (WithDefault, WithValidate, WithHelp, WithTransform, WithFilter, WithPageSize, WithContext, WithStdio, WithIcons). Structured Ask() API fills struct fields by name via reflect. Question/Prompt interface. Built-in validators (Required, MinLength, MaxLength, MinItems, MaxItems, MatchRegex, ComposeValidators). Transformers (Title, ToLower, ToUpper, ComposeTransformers).

Internal packages: internal/term (raw mode via POSIX termios on Darwin/Linux, Windows Console API, ANSI escape helpers), internal/keys (key event parser, line editor).

Compat layers: compat/survey (drop-in for survey/v2 — Input/Password/Confirm/Select/MultiSelect/Multiline/Editor structs, Ask/AskOne, validators, transformers, IconSet), compat/promptui (Prompt struct with Label/Default/Validate/Mask/IsConfirm, Select struct with Label/Items/Size/Templates/Searcher).

136 tests across 5 packages. CI green on Go 1.22+1.23 + golangci-lint. MIT license.

